data.description: Do you want to live in a small, quiet town like Garrettsville? Here's your chance! When you walk in through the one car garage to find the open concept kitchen and dining room with a sliding glass doors leading onto the back deck, overlooking the scenic backyard. Off the dining room, you'll see a large living room with the front door that goes out to your front porch. Down the hall is three spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom. The walk out  basement is finished and includes a large family room, laundry room, a half bath, AND a patio leading out to a large backyard! Sitting on three acres this home has so much potential! Call for a private showing today!
